OL,3,CConsumer confidence sees six-point
OL,4,C'Burnham bounce'
OL,6,FConsumer confidence has seen a
OL,7,Fsignificant six-point "Burnham bounce"
OL,8,F` the largest increase since November
OL,9,F2023.
OL,11,FGfK said the heatwaves, football
OL,12,Fsuccess and a new Prime Minister
OL,13,Fappeared to have "lifted the mood",
OL,14,Falbeit the headline figure remaining
OL,15,Ffirmly in negative territory at minus
OL,16,F17.
OL,26,@oD@WOUoD@fO]uD@ROUuD@bO]
