OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784852297
OL,3,CConsumer confidence sees six-point
OL,4,C'Burnham bounce'
OL,6,FConfidence in the country's general
OL,7,Feconomic situation over the last 12
OL,8,Fmonths jumped by 10 points to minus 39
OL,9,F` five points higher than a year ago `
OL,10,Fwhile expectations for the economy
OL,11,Fover the coming 12 months rose by
OL,12,Feight points to minus 28 ` one point
OL,13,Fabove last July.
OL,15,FThe Major Purchase Index, an indicator
OL,16,Fof confidence in buying big ticket
OL,17,Fitems, also saw an eight-point
OL,18,Fincrease to minus 12, three points
OL,19,Fhigher than July last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
