OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784852297
OL,3,CConsumer confidence sees six-point
OL,4,C'Burnham bounce'
OL,6,FConfidence in personal finances over
OL,7,Fthe next year is up three points,
OL,8,Fdragging the measure into positive
OL,9,Fterritory at one, but one point lower
OL,10,Fthan last July.
OL,12,FThe survey was taken between July 1
OL,13,Fand July 14, ahead of Mr Burnham
OL,14,Fwalking into Number 10 on July 20 and
OL,15,Fmaking any policy announcements.
OL,17,FNeil Bellamy, consumer insights
OL,18,Fdirector at GfK, said: "Hot on the
OL,19,Fheels of the summer heatwaves, July
OL,20,Fhas delivered a wave of optimism.
OL,26,@zD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784852297
OL,3,CConsumer confidence sees six-point
OL,4,C'Burnham bounce'
OL,6,F"The sense of a fresh start following
OL,7,Fthe appointment of a new Prime
OL,8,FMinister surely accounts for some of
OL,9,Fthis bounce.
OL,11,F"There were also hopes at the start of
OL,12,FJuly that the Middle East conflict
OL,13,Fmight stabilise and bring UK fuel
OL,14,Fprices down.
OL,16,F"The feel-good factor of the Fifa
OL,17,FWorld Cup will have reinforced
OL,18,Fsentiment too.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
