OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784852297
OL,3,CConsumer confidence sees six-point
OL,4,C'Burnham bounce'
OL,6,F"However, July's improved Overall
OL,7,FIndex Score remains within the narrow
OL,8,Frange seen since the end of 2023, and
OL,9,Fit is a decade since the headline
OL,10,Fscore was in positive territory.
OL,12,F"For the 'Burnham bounce' to be
OL,13,Fsustainable and boost consumer
OL,14,Fconfidence, it will require consistent
OL,15,Fdelivery by the refreshed UK
OL,16,FGovernment against deep cost-of-living
OL,17,Fchallenges and persistent low economic
OL,18,Fgrowth."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@HO]
